                                        </li>

                                        <li>
                                            Make navigation easier by preventing you from having to re-enter
                                            the same information while moving between pages.
                                        </li>
                                    </ul>
                                </div>

                                <p>
                                    To protect your privacy, please ensure that you close your browser completely
                                    after completing your session on websites that use cookies.
                                </p>

                                <p class="mb-0">
                                    If you are concerned about cookies, you can configure your browser settings
                                    to notify you before accepting cookies. Most modern browsers provide options
                                    to view, manage, or disable cookies.
                                </p>
